'''雷克沙'''（Lexar）是一家由深圳市江波龙电子有限公司持有的生产多种[[数位媒体|数位媒体]]与软件的[[美国|美国]]制造商，总部位于[[加州|加州]][[費利蒙_(美國加州)|费利蒙]]。生产的媒体包括[[SD卡|SD卡]]、[[Memory_Stick|Memory Stick]]、[[隨身碟|隨身碟]]与[[CompactFlash|CompactFlash]]卡，另有生产读卡机与[[MP3播放器|MP3播放器]]。他们亦有生产适用于[[PlayStation_Portable|PSP]]版本的[[Memory_Stick_Duo|Memory Stick Duo]]，当中包含了其中一版的Xploder。他们某些记忆卡被认为是市面上最快的产品。雷克沙曾是[[思睿逻辑|思睿逻辑]]的一个部门，充分利用了其母公司在建设ATA控制器上的经验来开发其自家的快闪存储器控制器。<ref>{{cite web|title=Lexar Adds Xploder Lite Software To Its Gaming Edition Memory Cards|url=http://www.lexar.com/about/newsroom/press-releases/lexar-adds-xploder-lite-software-its-gaming-edition-memory-cards|publisher=Lexar Media, Inc|accessdate=10 November 2013|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131110214210/http://www.lexar.com/about/newsroom/press-releases/lexar-adds-xploder-lite-software-its-gaming-edition-memory-cards|archive-date=2013-11-10|url-status=yes}}</ref>雷克沙于1996年自思睿逻辑分拆。<ref>{{cite web|title=Lexar Media Holds The Right Cards|url=https://www.forbes.com/2003/04/10/cx_ah_0410flash.html|publisher=Forbes.com LLC|accessdate=10 November 2013|archive-date=2020-08-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200815152337/https://www.forbes.com/2003/04/10/cx_ah_0410flash.html|dead-url=no}}</ref> 

2005年，雷克沙在一场针对[[东芝|东芝]][[抄袭|抄袭]]雷克沙闪存技术的诉讼中被判賠3.8亿美元<ref name="Photography Blog" /><ref>{{cite web| url=http://www.bizjournals.com/sanjose/stories/2005/03/21/daily32.html| title=Lexar wins patent suit against Toshiba| date=March 23, 2005| publisher=Silicon Valley Business Journal| access-date=October 7, 2015}}</ref>2006年，雷克沙被[[美光科技|美光科技]]收购<ref>{{Cite press release|url=https://www.businesswire.com/news/home/20060621005878/en/Micron-Technology-Lexar-Media-Announce-Completion-Transaction|title=Micron Technology, Inc., and Lexar Media, Inc. Announce Completion of Transaction|date=21 June 2006|access-date=28 October 2018|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170309054201/https://www.businesswire.com/news/home/20060621005878/en/Micron-Technology-Lexar-Media-Announce-Completion-Transaction|archive-date=2017-03-09|dead-url=no}}</ref>，随后雷克沙以美光[[子公司|子公司]][[雷克沙媒体|雷克沙媒体]]（Lexar Media, Inc.）的名义与关键科技合并。2007年9月，雷克沙延长了与[[伊士曼柯达公司|伊士曼柯达公司]]的协议，在全球范围内开发和销售柯达品牌的闪存产品。<ref>{{cite web|title=Kodak and Lexar Announce New Extended Five-Year Agreement|date=4 September 2007|url=http://www.businesswire.com/news/home/20070904005281/en/Kodak-Lexar-Announce-Extended-Five-Year-Agreement|publisher=Business Wire|accessdate=10 November 2013|archive-date=2018-10-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181029071539/https://www.businesswire.com/news/home/20070904005281/en/Kodak-Lexar-Announce-Extended-Five-Year-Agreement|dead-url=no}}</ref>

Lexar JumpDrive商标在首次采用USB闪存驱动器时经常与术语同义使用。

2017年6月26日，美光科技宣布停止雷克沙零售可移动媒体存储业务，并将部分或全部业务出售。<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.micron.com/about/blogs/2017/june/micron-discontinuing-lexar-removable-storage-retail-business|title=Micron Technology, Inc. - Micron Discontinuing Lexar Removable Storage Retail Business|last=Hawkins|first=Jay|date=26 June 2017|website=Micron.com|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170825023032/https://www.micron.com/about/blogs/2017/june/micron-discontinuing-lexar-removable-storage-retail-business|archive-date=2017-08-25|url-status=no|access-date=24 August 2017}}</ref>

2017年8月31日，雷克沙被中国深圳闪存公司深圳市江波龙电子有限公司收购。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.longsys.com/longsys-acquires-lexar-brand-a-leading-brand-for-high-performance-removable-storage-solutions/|title=Longsys Acquires Lexar Brand, a Leading Brand for High-Performance Removable Storage Solutions|date=31 August 2017|website=Longsys.com|access-date=13 September 2017|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170901160044/http://www.longsys.com/longsys-acquires-lexar-brand-a-leading-brand-for-high-performance-removable-storage-solutions/|archive-date=2017-09-01|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2018年，雷克沙重新进入闪存市场。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.theverge.com/circuitbreaker/2018/8/17/17724060/lexar-flash-storage-return|title=Lexar's making a glorious return to the world of flash storage|first=Shoshana|last=Wodinsky|date=17 August 2018|website=The Verge|accessdate=27 April 2019|archive-date=2020-11-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201109014629/https://www.theverge.com/circuitbreaker/2018/8/17/17724060/lexar-flash-storage-return|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2019年1月，该公司推出了第一张存储容量为1TB（TB）的SD卡。<ref>{{cite news |title=Lexar Announces 1TB 633x SDXC UHS-I card, the behemoth of storage capacity. |url=http://www.lexar.com/lexar-announces-1tb-633x-sdxc-uhs-i-card-the-behemoth-of-storage-capacity/ |date=9 January 2019 |work=Lexar |accessdate=10 January 2019 |archive-date=2020-11-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201112030323/https://www.lexar.com/lexar-announces-1tb-633x-sdxc-uhs-i-card-the-behemoth-of-storage-capacity/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>

2019年12月，雷克沙展示了7.5GB/s PCIe 4.0 SSD原型，该原型将成为世界上最快的消费SSD。<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://blocksandfiles.com/2019/12/17/lexar-pcie-4-0-ssd/|title=Lexar demos world's fastest consumer SSD|last=Mellor|first=Chris|date=2019-12-17|website=Blocks and Files|language=en-GB|access-date=2020-02-21|archive-date=2020-10-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201024005944/https://blocksandfiles.com/2019/12/17/lexar-pcie-4-0-ssd/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.pcmag.com/news/lexar-is-testing-a-7gbs-pcie-ssd|title=Lexar Is Testing a 7GB/s PCIe SSD|website=PCMAG|language=en|access-date=2020-02-21|archive-date=2021-04-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210424061014/https://www.pcmag.com/news/lexar-is-testing-a-7gbs-pcie-ssd|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2020年4月，雷克沙发布了其世界上最小的存储卡（nCARD），该存储卡采用长江存储技术（YMTC）的Xtacking技术。<ref>{{cite news |title=Longsys & Yangtze Memory Technologies Revealed the World's Smallest MicroSD Card |url=https://www.gadgetsay.com/longsys-electronics-yangtze-river-storage-revealed-the-worlds-smallest-microsd-card/ |date=21 April 2020 |work=Gadgetsay |accessdate=24 April 2020 |archive-date=2020-10-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201024093908/https://www.gadgetsay.com/longsys-electronics-yangtze-river-storage-revealed-the-worlds-smallest-microsd-card/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>

2020年6月，雷克沙宣布进入DRAM市场，为主流笔记本电脑和台式机推出了七款不同的DDR4-2666内存套件。雷克沙还计划在未来发布更快的3000MHz和3200MHz内存套件，以及“带散热片和RGB照明”的套件，针对玩家和爱好者。<ref>{{cite news |title=Lexar launches its first-ever DRAM kits, promises faster RAM is coming |url=https://www.pcgamer.com/lexar-launches-its-first-ever-dram-kits-promises-faster-ram-is-coming/ |date=19 June 2020 |work=PC Gamer |accessdate=21 June 2020 |archive-date=2021-02-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210214095411/https://www.pcgamer.com/lexar-launches-its-first-ever-dram-kits-promises-faster-ram-is-coming/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>

